## Commands

Both projects share the same npm scripts. Run from inside the project directory:

```bash
# Development server
cd wegrow && npm run serve      # → http://localhost:8080
cd farmwatch && npm run serve   # → http://localhost:8081

# Production build (outputs to dist/)
npm run build
```

Node.js is installed at `C:\Program Files\nodejs`. If `npm` is not on PATH in a new shell:
```bash
export PATH="/c/Program Files/nodejs:$PATH"
```

No test runner is configured in either project.

