## Architecture

### Shared Stack (both projects)
- **Vue 2.6** + **Vue Router 3** (hash mode) + **Vuex 3**
- **Element UI 2.15** — all form controls, tables, dialogs, layout grid
- **ECharts 5.4** — all charts; always init in `mounted()` via `this.$nextTick`, always destroy in `beforeDestroy()`, always add `window.addEventListener('resize', ...)` handler
- **Axios 0.27** — all HTTP via `src/api/request.js` instance

### wegrow

**Backend:** `https://appapi.fufluns.net` (all endpoints POST). Routes match the live site's URL structure exactly (e.g. `/#/dataAnalysisSystem/dataAnalysisSystem`).

**Auth:** Token stored in `localStorage` as `wegrow_token`. On 401 the interceptor clears the token and redirects to `/#/login`. Login falls back to demo mode (any credentials accepted, roles set to `['admin']`) if the API is unreachable.

**Role-gating:** The `writeDeviceId` route has `meta.permissions: ['admin','ROLE_device_manager','ROLE_admin']`. The layout reads `store.getters['user/roles']` to conditionally render the HUB 生產工具 nav item.

**Vuex:** Single `user` module (namespaced). Getters: `user/token`, `user/userInfo`, `user/roles`.

**API modules** in `src/api/`:
- `user.js` — login, logout, getUserInfo, getUserList
- `hub.js` — getHubInfoFamily, getHubByUserName, getHubHistory, exportHubHistory, notifications
- `farm.js` — full CRUD for `/farm/*` and `/greenhouse/*`, plus gateway/controller endpoints
- `weather.js` — QWeather GEO + 7-day forecast (API key placeholder in this file)

### farmwatch

**Backend:** `http://localhost:3000/api` (placeholder; not yet connected to real IoT API). The Axios error interceptor returns `null` instead of rejecting, so **every view must check for null and fall back to mock data**.

**Mock data** lives entirely in `src/utils/mock.js`:
- `mockFarms` — array of 4 farm objects with full sensor readings, pest status, alerts, yield predictions
- `generateHistory(baseValue, variance, hours)` — generates hourly time-series for charts
- `generateYieldHistory()` — monthly actual vs. predicted series
- `mockHarvestHistory`, `pestEvents` — static arrays for tables/timelines
- `TODAY = new Date('2026-03-26')`, `getDaysUntil(dateStr)` — date helpers

**Auth:** Token in `localStorage` as `farmwatch_token`. Demo login: `admin` / `1234` (handled entirely in the Login view; no real auth endpoint exists yet).

**Vuex:** Flat store (not namespaced modules). State: `token`, `user`, `farms`, `alerts`. Getters: `isLoggedIn`, `userName`, `dangerFarms`, `warningFarms`.

**Reusable components** in `src/components/`:
- `SensorCard.vue` — props: `label, value, unit, icon, status`
- `FarmStatusBadge.vue` — props: `status` (`'healthy'|'warning'|'danger'`)
- `HarvestCountdown.vue` — props: `targetDate, cropName`
- `AlertItem.vue` — props: `type, message, time, farmName`

**Farm detail routing:** `src/views/farm-detail/index.vue` reads `this.$route.params.id`, finds the matching farm from `mockFarms` (numeric id match).

